# AI Document Chatbot with Flask

A Flask-based web application that allows users to upload documents (PDF or text) and ask questions about the content using OpenAI's GPT models and FAISS for vector search.

## Features

- Document upload (PDF and text files)
- Text extraction and preprocessing
- Vector embeddings using OpenAI's API
- Semantic search with FAISS
- Context-aware Q&A using GPT-3.5/GPT-4

## Tech Stack

- **Backend**: Python, Flask
- **AI/NLP**: OpenAI API, LangChain
- **Vector Database**: FAISS
- **Frontend**: HTML, CSS (Tailwind), JavaScript

